commonly used force fields. A new pair potential for the water--carbon
non-covalent component of the interaction has been built and it is recommended
for molecular dynamics simulation involving graphdiyne and water.},
 author = {Bartolomei, Massimiliano and Carmona-Novillo, Estela and Hernández, Marta I. and Campos-Martínez, José and Pirani, Fernando and Giorgi, Giacomo and Yamashita, Koichi},
