ions involving oriented chiral molecules and linearly or circularly polarized radiation. This work is in progress in our laboratory.},
 author = {Falcinelli, Stefano and Rosi, Marzio and Pirani, Fernando and Bassi, Davide and Alagia, Michele and Schio, Luca and Richter, Robert and Stranges, Stefano and Balucani, Nadia and Lorent, Vincent and Vecchiocattivi, Franco},
